rows.label: qst701904_msg0001
rows.name:
Adel-sama, everyone. The Invidian
expedition has returned

rows.label: qst701904_msg0002
rows.name: Did everyone make it back safely?

rows.label: qst701904_msg0003
rows.name: Yes. Everyone is accounted for.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0004
rows.name: Phew! That's a relief.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0005
rows.name:
I hadn't quite expected them to be
back so quickly.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0006
rows.name:
That's because they had
such a good helmswoman! â™ª

rows.label: qst701904_msg0007
rows.name: Thanks, Maquia.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0008
rows.name:
Pfft, don't mention it! Gotta take on a
few challenges from time to time to
keep the old skills up to scratch.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0009
rows.name:
Ah yeah, our fearless leader has
the goods you were after.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0101
rows.name:
Hey. Looks like we made it back
in one piece.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0102
rows.name:
Of course we got the Dragon Incense.
Rita managed to find some really
high-quality stuff, too.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0103
rows.name:
There's more to that kid than I thought.
She'll make an excellent adventurer
someday, mark my words.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0104
rows.name:
Looks like we made the right choice
in picking you to lead.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0105
rows.name:
Totally. Thank you, Dio. And
everyone else too, of course.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0201
rows.name: We're baaack!

rows.label: qst701904_msg0202
rows.name:
I really do love exploring.
Invidia's Divine Beast is GORGEOUS.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0203
rows.name:
I kept going off to explore. I think
the others got a bit annoyed by it,
to tell you the truth.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0204
rows.name:
But I found the Dragon Incense
we were looking for, so yay!

rows.label: qst701904_msg0205
rows.name: Everyone does look slightly...frazzled.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0206
rows.name: Thank you, Rita.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0301
rows.name:
Time for friends to reconsider harsh
judgement of Ryuuryuu!

rows.label: qst701904_msg0302
rows.name:
We got Dragon Incense and came
back! And nobody dead.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0303
rows.name: All thanks to brave leader Ryuuryuu!

rows.label: qst701904_msg0304
rows.name:
Someone telling sneaky lie-lies!
Kachakacha is one who find
Dragon Incense!

rows.label: qst701904_msg0305
rows.name: No, it Yokuyoku!

rows.label: qst701904_msg0306
rows.name: No! Biggest bro make terrible leader!

rows.label: qst701904_msg0307
rows.name:
Cease this trivial bickering in front
of Emperor Hugo.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0309
rows.name: Thank you for your service, guys.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0401
rows.name: I am STARVING. Got anything to eat?

rows.label: qst701904_msg0402
rows.name:
Oh, wait, before I sit down for some
grub, I should hand over this Dragon
Incense.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0403
rows.name:
It was a bloody hard time, I hope you
know. Wrangling those Nopon and that
singing buffoon was extremely trying.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0404
rows.name: I can well imagine.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0405
rows.name: Thank you, Augusto.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0501
rows.name:
Hey! Look, we made it back safe
and sound.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0502
rows.name:
First, let me tell you all about "the
conversation" with Deetta.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0503
rows.name: How about another time?

rows.label: qst701904_msg0504
rows.name:
Oh. OK.
It's a good story. You're missing out.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0505
rows.name:
Anyway, here's the Dragon Incense
you asked for. The Dragon's Stomach
is a horrid, squishy kind of place.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0506
rows.name: Thank you, Leo!

rows.label: qst701904_msg0601
rows.name: Morumo so tired...

rows.label: qst701904_msg0602
rows.name:
Everyone so independent, was very
tricky to work together.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0603
rows.name:
Augusto not work if hungry, Rita
always wander off if not keep eye
on her...

rows.label: qst701904_msg0604
rows.name:
But somehow at end of it all, we find
high-grade Dragon Incense.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0605
rows.name:
It sounds like your experience as
chairman served you well.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0606
rows.name: Indeed. Thank you, Morumo!

rows.label: qst701904_msg0701
rows.name: I was thinking, Laura-sama

rows.label: qst701904_msg0702
rows.name:
It seems like everybody we met so far
came to help us out.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0703
rows.name: Isn't it marvelous?

rows.label: qst701904_msg0704
rows.name: You're right. Wow.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0053
rows.name:
The camera shows the faces of the
NPCs. About 3 cuts, maybe more.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0705
rows.name: It's pretty incredible.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0706
rows.name: My heart's so full I could cry.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0707
rows.name: Not again...

rows.label: qst701904_msg0708
rows.name: You cry way too easily.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0709
rows.name:
There's no denying that, but I feel it
might be somewhat justified this time.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0710
rows.name:
All the people our journey has
intertwined with, coming together to
lend their strength to a common cause.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0711
rows.name:
That's the power of community
spirit for you.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0712
rows.name:
Community spirit...
Now that's a nice phrase.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0713
rows.name: I should write it down in my journal.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0714
rows.name:
I imagine you've had an awful lot
to write about, Kagutsuchi.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0715
rows.name: Hah. You could say that.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0716
rows.name:
But it isn't all war and death.
Much of it has been good.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0717
rows.name: Indeed.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0718
rows.name:
I feel like every day I'm seeing and
experiencing new things.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0719
rows.name: That's great.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0720
rows.name: Yeah... I suppose it is.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0070
rows.name:
Laura is happy that Shin is experiencing
happy days.
There's a small pause

rows.label: qst701904_msg0721
rows.name:
We need to deliver this Dragon Incense.
There's a little girl who's waiting for us.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0722
rows.name:
You're right. There's not a
moment to lose.

rows.label: qst701904_msg0723
rows.name: The capital, then.
